  "prompt": "How can I convert YouTube videos to MP3 on my iPhone?",
  "response": "To convert YouTube videos to MP3 on your iPhone, you can use third-party apps or online services. Here are a few methods:\n\n### **Method 1: Using a Third-Party App**\n1. **Download a YouTube to MP3 Converter App**:\n   - Search for apps like **MediaConvert**, **Documents by Readdle**, or **MP3 Converter** in the App Store.\n   - Download and install the app.\n\n2. **Copy the YouTube Video URL**:\n   - Open the YouTube app or website in Safari.\n   - Find the video you want to convert and tap the **Share** button.\n   - Choose **Copy Link** to copy the video URL.\n\n3. **Paste the URL in the Converter App**:\n   - Open the converter app you installed.\n   - Paste the copied YouTube link into the app\u2019s search or URL field.\n   - Select **Convert to MP3** or a similar option.\n\n4. **Download the MP3 File**:\n   - Once the conversion is complete, the app will allow you to download or save the MP3 file to your iPhone.\n\n5. **Access the MP3 File**:\n   - The file will usually be saved in the app\u2019s local storage. You can transfer it to the **Files** app or export it to other apps like Apple Music.\n\n---\n\n### **Method 2: Using Online Services**\n1. **Copy the YouTube Video URL**:\n   - Open YouTube and copy the link of the video you want to convert (as described above).\n\n2. **Use an Online Converter**:\n   - Open Safari and go to an online converter website like **ytmp3.cc**, **y2mate.com**, or **onlinevideoconverter.com**.\n   - Paste the YouTube URL into the website\u2019s input field.\n\n3. **Convert and Download**:\n   - Select the **MP3** option and start the conversion process.\n   - Once the conversion is complete, tap the **Download** button to save the MP3 file to your iPhone.\n\n4. **Save the MP3 File**:\n   - The file will download to your iPhone\u2019s **Downloads** folder or the **Files** app.\n\n---\n\n### **Method 3: Using Shortcuts (iOS Automation)**\n1. **Download a YouTube to MP3 Shortcut**:\n   - Open Safari and search for a YouTube to MP3 shortcut (e.g., from **RoutineHub** or other sources).\n   - Download and add the shortcut to your Shortcuts app.\n\n2. **Copy the YouTube Video URL**:\n   - Copy the link of the YouTube video (as described above).\n\n3. **Run the Shortcut**:\n   - Open the Shortcuts app and run the YouTube to MP3 shortcut.\n   - Paste the URL when prompted, and the shortcut will download the MP3 file.\n\n4. **Save the MP3 File**:\n   - The file will be saved to your **Files** app or another designated location.\n\n---\n\n### **Important Notes**:\n- Be cautious about copyright laws and only download videos you have the right to convert.\n- Use trusted apps and websites to avoid malware or unwanted ads.\n- Some methods might not work if YouTube changes their policies or APIs.\n\nLet me know if you need further assistance!",
